snippet.title: Liberty Forum
snippet.description:
The mission of The Liberty Forum of Silicon Valley is to promote the principles of American liberty through education.  As the recognized non-partisan umbrella organization in the Bay Area, we are the place for fans of liberty from Silicon Valley and beyond to gather, share ideas and become empowered.

This channel provides videos of speakers from our monthly meetings and The Right Side cable access show.
